0bsimple as:\r\n```\r\n$ git clone https://github.com/spack/spack.git\r\n$ . spack/share/spack/setup-env.sh\r\n$ spack install py-datalad\r\n```\r\nor\r\n```\r\n$ spack install py-datalad@0.14.6\r\n```\r\nto install an older version. \u200bThis will also install git-annex as a dependency.\r\n\r\nTo use it:\r\n```\r\n$ spack load py-datalad\r\n```\r\n\r\ndatalad packages available in spack so far:\r\n- `py-datalad`\r\n- `py-datalad-container`\r\n- `py-datalad-hirni`\r\n- `py-datalad-metalad`\r\n- `py-datalad-neuroimaging`\r\n- `py-datalad-webapp`", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/6040/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/datalad/datalad/issues/6040/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null}